OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,FThailand's Princess Bajrakitiyabha
OL,7,FMahidol, a lawyer and the eldest of
OL,8,FKing Maha Vajiralongkorn's children,
OL,9,Fhas died at 47, the Bureau of the
OL,10,FRoyal Household said.
OL,12,FShe died on Thursday evening at a
OL,13,FBangkok hospital where she had been
OL,14,Fcared for since falling unconscious
OL,15,Fdue to illness three years ago,
OL,16,Faccording to the statement issued
OL,17,FFriday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
