OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,F"This loss is not merely bad news
OL,7,Fannounced to the people, but an
OL,8,Fimmeasurable grief in the hearts of
OL,9,Fthe entire nation," Prime Minister
OL,10,FAnutin Charnvirakul said in a
OL,11,Ftelevised speech.
OL,13,FHe said the princess was "a pride of
OL,14,FThailand," and that "her commitment to
OL,15,Fbuilding a society of kindness,
OL,16,Fjustice, and equality, will forever
OL,17,Fremain as a moral legacy for the
OL,18,Fnation, a guiding light for
OL,19,Fgenerations of Thais."
