OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,FA small group of mourners gathered in
OL,7,Fan atrium at King Chulalongkorn
OL,8,FMemorial Hospital, where the princess
OL,9,Fhad been treated. Most held framed or
OL,10,Flaminated photos of her throughout the
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FBajrakitiyabha was active in justice
OL,14,Freform efforts and best known for her
OL,15,FKamlangjai, or "Inspire," project to
OL,16,Fhelp rehabilitate incarcerated Thai
OL,17,Fwomen ahead of their release.
OL,26,@wD@POUwD@YO]
