OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,FShe was hospitalised in December 2022
OL,7,Fafter falling unconscious while
OL,8,Ftraining dogs for an army exhibition.
OL,9,FThe palace said she had a mycoplasma
OL,10,Finfection, a bacterial infection
OL,11,Fusually associated with pneumonia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
