OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,FThe princess was born on December 7,
OL,7,F1978, to Vajiralongkorn, who was the
OL,8,Fcrown prince at the time, and his then-
OL,9,Fwife, Princess Soamsawali.
OL,10,FVajiralongkorn has seven children by
OL,11,Fthree of his four successive wives.
OL,12,FBajrakitiyabha was also known by the
OL,13,Froyal name Bajrakitiyabha Narendira
OL,14,FDebyavati, used in formal state
OL,15,Fsettings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
