OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,FPrince Dipangkorn Rasmijoti, the
OL,7,Fyoungest of the king's children, is
OL,8,Fthe presumptive heir because sons take
OL,9,Fprecedence in Thailand's line of
OL,10,Fsuccession. But Bajrakitiyabha's
OL,11,Fexperience in public service raised
OL,12,Fspeculation she was set to hold an
OL,13,Fimportant role in any future
OL,14,Fsuccession, perhaps as regent to a
OL,15,Fyouthful monarch.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
