PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,FBajrakitiyabha studied law at
OL,7,FThammasat University then went to
OL,8,FCornell University in New York state,
OL,9,Fwhere she earned a master's degree in
OL,10,Flaw and a doctorate.
OL,12,FAfter working briefly at the Thai
OL,13,FMission to the UN in New York City,
OL,14,Fshe returned home and worked as a
OL,15,Fpublic prosecutor. She renewed her
OL,16,Fdiplomatic career with an appointment
OL,17,Fas Thailand's ambassador to Austria
OL,18,Ffrom 2012 to 2014 before returning to
OL,19,Fher homeland to concentrate on
OL,20,Fcriminal justice issues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
