OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781280694
OL,3,CThai princess dies aged 47, after
OL,4,Cthree years in a coma
OL,6,FIn 2017 she was appointed a goodwill
OL,7,Fambassador for the UN Office on Drugs
OL,8,Fand Crime.
OL,10,FIn addition to working for the
OL,11,Frehabilitation of female convicts, she
OL,12,Fwas involved in other projects
OL,13,Fincluding a campaign to enhance the
OL,14,Fliving conditions of women prisoners
OL,15,Fand promoting efforts to stem violence
OL,16,Fagainst women as an honorary UN
OL,17,Fgoodwill ambassador for women. Her
OL,18,Fefforts led to the U.N. General
OL,19,FAssembly adopting the "Bangkok Rules"
OL,20,Fon care and conditions for female
OL,21,Fprisoners.
